    "description": "<p><strong>GENERAL RAIL TECHNOLOGY PRIVATE LIMITED</strong> is a leading provider specializing in the design, development, and installation of platform screen door (PSD) systems for rail transit networks. Our expertise spans the entire lifecycle of PSD systems, including research and development, production, sales, installation, technical services, and maintenance. We are committed to delivering innovative and reliable solutions that enhance safety and efficiency in railway operations.</p>\n<p>With a focus on integrating cutting-edge technologies into modern urban rail infrastructures, we collaborate closely with stakeholders and partners worldwide. Our goal is to contribute to the development of smarter, safer public transportation systems.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At <strong>GENERAL RAIL TECHNOLOGY PRIVATE LIMITED</strong>, we value excellence and innovation. We are always seeking talented individuals who share our vision and are passionate about shaping the future of rail transit.</p>",
